{"tid":747890,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"愛簡單了 [原創歌曲]","createTime":"2018-07-18T17:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T18:20:19.000Z","uid":190992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43b32821968b4894a95e0dbe1e544d06a55f2013","tid":747890,"uid":190992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T17:58:54.000Z","msg":"第一首發佈的原創歌曲, 記錄了&quot;當告別是吻我那刻開始&quot;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0LktHKvgayM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0LktHKvgayM&d=mQ4zCnXyZ2L3UsRAqs88lS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=bfaa6a37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0LktHKvgayM</a><br />\n<br />\n　愛簡單了 [原創歌曲]<br />\n　作曲/填詞/主唱: 夢詞人<br />\n<br />\n　花了多少工作天<br />\n　在耗盡努力去追逐愛戀<br />\n　願我在有效時間<br />\n　築建的天空終於完成　尋覓求真愛<br />\n　愛多次　痛多次　會等下次<br />\n　最怕錯過多一次<br />\n　是那一位擦過身邊心中天使<br />\n<br />\n＃分秒間多少掛牽<br />\n　突發事也令愛可能變遷<br />\n　狀態大勇亦難免<br />\n　因愛輸不起啞口無言　無限期開戰<br />\n　愛一次　痛千次　再拖十次<br />\n　哪裏有存在意義<br />\n　當告別時吻我那刻開始<br />\n<br />\n＊你說愛簡單了<br />\n　奈何我怕愛真的不渺小<br />\n　覓到真愛又怕失去天高海闊使我動搖<br />\n　不禁心驚膽吊<br />\n　你叫我心死了<br />\n　奈何你對我卻是最重要<br />\n　為愛總會歇斯底里錯綜交錯真的要想想<br />\n　最佳方法了<br />\n<br />\n　重複　＃　＊<br />\n<br />\n　只想此刻挽著你手<br />\n　變簡單了<br />\n　每刻都想挽著你手<br />\n　太簡單了<br />\n<br />\n　愛簡單了,#原創,#粵語歌,#【我敢唱】發SING大比拼,#EP,#情歌,#我的最愛,#2004,#比賽,#YouTube影片,#夢詞人頻道,#廣東歌,#cantopop,#music,#song,#songs,#melody,#newsong<br />\n<br />\n　夢詞人 <a href=\"https://linktr.ee/dreaminglyricist\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flinktr.ee%2Fdreaminglyricist&d=mQ4zCnXyZ2L3UsRAqs88lS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=63fa55f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://linktr.ee/dreaminglyricist</a>"},{"pid":"07985ae438fc25c1016f04e89680246ce97d1390","tid":747890,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T18:20:19.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}